b嘅例牌happy bday<br />\n感覺上好似無人關心自己咁<br />\n我同自己講咗好多次<br />\n無期望就無失望<br />\n但始終未做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc94af0d9f8f9a1d6196d8167ca46693b22cc961","tid":877860,"uid":507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T17:01:51.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係hide返工個幾個鐘<br />\n都係未夠膽全日hide"},{"pid":"47d0f88881f31766a81096e1feaf64389fe6e408","tid":877860,"uid":56610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T17:03:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大個仔 唔再過生日lu</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1806c26ab23e8391f7e247fe0f83d92bbe05d8b3","tid":877860,"uid":28694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T17:04:49.000Z","msg":"最慘係冇hide都冇人同你講生日快樂 <br />\nHide唔hide其實都一樣 有心嘅話同你慶生添啦"},{"pid":"6ba3266daf21f49907e574bb0fff0adc1dd2856d","tid":877860,"uid":507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T17:05:52.000Z","msg":"始終放唔低囉"},{"pid":"a3eb82f0cfa01abd04031b4de6f18c6206453641","tid":877860,"uid":186035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T17:07:22.000Z","msg":"有時會諗究竟係咪因爲自己做人太失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}